/* For Netlify, Render, Vercel, etc. */
/* If using Vercel, use vercel.json rewrites instead */
/* If using Render, use render.yaml rewrites */
/* For Netlify: */
/* /index.html is your SPA entry point */
/* /api/* routes are NOT redirected */

/* Actual rule: */
/* All requests except /api/* go to index.html */
/* If you have other static assets, adjust as needed */

